title: Understanding Descriptive Analysis
text: Descriptive analysis focuses on summarizing past data to understand what has happened.

title: Purpose of Descriptive Analysis
text: The main goal of descriptive analysis is to provide insights into historical data patterns.

title: Characteristics of Descriptive Analysis
text: Descriptive analysis often involves the use of charts, graphs, and tables to present data.

title: Comparison with Other Analyses
text: Unlike predictive analysis, descriptive analysis does not attempt to forecast future outcomes.

title: Descriptive Analysis in Practice
text: In practice, descriptive analysis helps in understanding the frequency and distribution of data points.
